These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
House: craftsman, farmhouse, cottage, futuristic, townhouse, cape-cod, victorian
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 2. the futuristic house is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 6. the american is on the right of the cottage house##1
 7. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the townhouse house and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
14. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
15. the townhouse house is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| House          | cottage    | craftsman    | farmhouse | cape-cod | futuristic | townhouse    | victorian |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

