.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, satire, animation, mystery, horror, epic
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching superhero movies##7
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 6. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
 7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person watching superhero movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person watching epic movies##6
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre    | epic  | satire | horror | animation | comedy     | mystery | superhero  |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | chess  | skydiving  | rock-climbing | hiking      | camping |

