 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in june##7
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
14. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
16. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
17. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
18. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
19. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

