 6. the pakistani is on the right of the dutch##1
 7. the polish is somewhere between the dutch and the indian##7
 8. the person who's sport is frenching is on the far left##1
 9. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
12. the french is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
13. the french is on the left of the australian##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the french##3
