 5. the thai is on the left of the nigerian##1
 6. the australian is the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 8. the fan of rock is not the australian##6
 9. the thai is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
