 4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the tiparillo-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##7
 7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is not the person driving the helicopter##6
