 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 4. the owner of the lizard is not the person who likes ebony##6
 5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lavender##5
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who likes ebony##7
 9. the person who likes blue is not the owner of the ferret##6
10. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the rat##7
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
14. the person who likes coral is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
15. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5

