 9. the accountant is on the right of the nurse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the musician##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the architect is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
14. the person who's birthday is in june is not the entrepreneur##6
15. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the lawyer and the architect##7
16. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
17. the lawyer is somewhere between the coach and the accountant##7

.:: Answer ::.
